  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The study includes 700 patients referred for colonoscopy are randomized to colonoscopy with
      or without endoguide.

      The study will investigate whether the endoguide improves success rate and the patient's
      perception of pain.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
